<br />\n<br />\n   剛衝出門口，碰巧巴拉巴迎面而來，肉體與肉體間發生了一次激烈的碰撞，還好巴拉巴擁有一副結實的身軀，把撞擊力卸了下來。<br />\n<br />\n  「走！走！廁所有鬼！」<br />\n大基哥面帶驚慌，用盡全身的力氣勸說道。"},{"pid":"4f3f00ab8d86d397dc665288b6fd8070a678d0b4","tid":1977445,"uid":172172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T00:38:23.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"eae876675e4fc4ad78d39bd7849277bde98d6c9c","tid":1977445,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T00:58:44.000Z","msg":"巴拉巴不以為意，甚至展示了黑人強大的天賦，當場rap歌一首：<br />\n<br />\n   「呦！廁所有鬼，我驚！我驚！我好驚！」<br />\n<br />\n    「驚佢條毛，一二三四五六七」<br />\n<br />\n   「驚佢條毛，七六五四三二一」<br />\n<br />\n大基哥目瞪口呆，不知他在唱什麼。"},{"pid":"7535513d29c2e73ed08f9fe09cdf099b53caaa7c","tid":1977445,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09d2e83ccacf50e1de8690ef3b1fd9a36f1ac318","tid":1977445,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65e93b3270114db71d215ec5b2a2340d51a5aa3a","tid":1977445,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cff310f6977ecd0c44626f23c9a3ea1eca6c859","tid":1977445,"uid":191300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T21:10:33.000Z","msg":"會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T21:19:35.000Z","msg":"咁唔追了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T21:23:00.000Z","msg":"咁唔會，等你追"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T18:50:10.000Z","msg":"追緊"},{"pid":"eda5f861104888d4285092b685dcc05adcddb883","tid":1977445,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T19:35:06.000Z","msg":"唱畢，往衛生間大步跨去，大基哥想拉都拉不住，也不敢跟上，只能眼睜睜看著他步入鬼地方。<br />\n<br />\n   「喂，基佬，一個人on居居企係門口自言自語做乜鳩」<br />\n<br />\n 大基哥背後，傳來一陣熟透的聲音，<br />\n<br />\n  「以為你撞鬼tim」那獨一無二的口音，伴隨著腳步聲，越來越近了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n    此刻，他臉色瞬間發青，並且屏住呼吸，身軀更是完全僵硬，連回頭的力氣都沒有，或者說，根本不敢回頭。"},{"pid":"1d27dfabb2166ebb43e66530e9b223514a9fdac7","tid":1977445,"uid":299134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T19:37:14.000Z","msg":"係深夜嘅文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85108ee7ecc01c25e0a06ae68775cc85b8ec165e","tid":1977445,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d27dfabb2166ebb43e66530e9b223514a9fdac7","tid":1977445,"uid":299134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T19:37:14.000Z","msg":"係深夜嘅文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T19:37:50.000Z","msg":"仲未訓呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9dfe022e8652f574fe08438a0df6b54727cf8d","tid":1977445,"uid":299134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85108ee7ecc01c25e0a06ae68775cc85b8ec165e","tid":1977445,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d27dfabb2166ebb43e66530e9b223514a9fdac7","tid":1977445,"uid":299134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T19:37:14.000Z","msg":"係深夜嘅文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T19:37:50.000Z","msg":"仲未訓呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T20:16:53.000Z","msg":"未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時瞓慣5點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}